#4300
Nastivier's Crypt ~
     This is a very large ancient crypt including an iron bound, wooden 
coffin resting atop a cold stone altar.  Blood-red candles adrip with molten
wax flicker and fight in an unfelt breeze in the still air.  Shadows dance
and flee from the changing light, rushing to hide in the ever changing shelter
producing erie manifestations from some nether dimension.  Any sound in the
death still air is warped into hideous renditions of their origins.  The 
dead watch the living with the hatred of those that have known life and now
fight to remove it.
~
