#4301
A large fissure~
The ground opens up into a very large fissure that goes deeper than the
eye can follow into the earth.  The rock is charred black by whatever
holocost tore the ground asunder creating the fissure.  The sides look
like one could possibly climb down, but at considerable risk to their health.
~
