#4303
A hidden cavern~
A hidden cavern possibly made by moving hot lava while the fissure was
being formed.  The floor is very uneven, with intricate dips and minor
crevasses threatening to engulf an ankle.  A musty smell rests heavily in
the air, and there are many bones on the floor picked clean, a harsh white
against the ever encompassing blackness.
