#4305
At the bottom of the fissure~
The bottom of the fissure is covered in bones, both big and small, from 
entities that did not survive the climb down its treacherous walls.  The
light above is almost non-existant, having been engulfed by the dark.  The
air is dead still, and warmer than expected.  It is possible to climb back
up the charred walls, and there is a tunnel leading off to the south.
~
