#4311
Main Hall~
This is what appears to be the main hall of the castle.  The high walls
converge to a point far above.  Small creatures flitter about at its heights,
making only barely audible sounds.  Small globes on the wall of a lighter
hue of grey appear to be the source of illumination of this large room.  
Triangular archways lead off to the north, south, east, and west.
